dc_title_s: Map of Allegany County showing the topography and election districts
dc_description_s: Shows the topography and election districts of Allegany County, Maryland. Waterways and man-made features such as roads, railroads, bridges, and buildings are indicated.|Map.; Title from cataloger.; Includes legend. Relief shown by contours and spot heights.|61 x 126 centimeters|Scale 1:62,500|General Map Collection
